Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.44,0:23:12.52,Songs,,0,0,0,,(cor) Always give my life! Always give my life to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:17.80,Songs,,0,0,0,,Always give my life! Always give my love to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:20.80,Songs,,0,0,0,,(noia) Son janai? Ima kara de mo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.08,0:23:26.12,Songs,,0,0,0,,Iin janai? Yareru koto!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:33.36,Songs,,0,0,0,,Omotta doori ni yatte miyou,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.56,0:23:36.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,kimi to deau made.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.84,0:23:40.76,Songs,,0,0,0,,Nani mo nakatta keredo...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.96,0:23:43.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,(cor) Me o tojite omou!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.60,0:23:48.20,Songs,,0,0,0,,Issho ni ikiru basho ga aru kara!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.40,0:23:54.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,Always, ai no mune ni yuuki o dashite,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.68,0:23:58.92,Songs,,0,0,0,,tatoe sore ga dame da to shite mo ne!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.12,0:24:05.04,Songs,,0,0,0,,No, sore dake ga jibun janai.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.24,0:24:10.20,Songs,,0,0,0,,Yes, kazamuki ga kawatta ima tobitatou!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.40,0:24:15.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,(cor) Always give my love. Always give my love to you!
